sd = SideDict()
assert sd.max_price() is None
sd[Price('100.0')] = 1
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.0')
sd[Price('99.99')] = 1
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.0')
sd[Price('100.001')] = 1
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.001')
sd[Price('100.02')] = 1
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.02')
sd[Price('100.02')] = 2
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.02')
sd[Price('100.001')] = 1
assert sd.max_price() == Price('100.02')
